  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-data-table\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-data-table/`\n\n### wc-mcp Tools — USE THESE FOR SCORING\n- `score_component`, `get_component`, `analyze_accessibility`, `validate_usage`, `list_css_parts`, `list_events`, `list_slots`, `get_design_tokens`\n- **Report any wc-mcp bugs to `/Volumes/Development/booked/wc-tools` board.**\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens. Row striping, header background, borders, selection highlight. Dark mode.\n2. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. Proper table semantics. Column headers (scope). Sort announcement. Row selection announcement. Keyboard navigation (grid pattern).\n3. **Functionality** — Sorting. Pagination integration. Row selection (single/multi). Column resize. Sticky header. Responsive (horizontal scroll or card view). Data binding.\n4. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`. Column definition types. Generic row type.\n5. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. CSS Parts (header, row, cell). Responsive strategy. Overflow handling.\n6. **CEM Accuracy** — Complex API fully documented.\n7. **Tests** — 80%+ coverage. Sorting. Selection. Keyboard navigation. Responsive.\n8. **Storybook** — Basic. Sortable. Selectable. Paginated. Responsive.\n9. **Drupal Compatibility** — Views table output. Twig-friendly. Dynamic data loading.\n10. **Portability** — CDN-ready. No external table lib.\n\n### Deliverable\nDetailed audit report. Fix CRITICAL+HIGH. Document rest.",
